00:35:28,905 --> 00:35:34,000
today marks the anniversary
of a very tragic event.

591
00:35:34,106 --> 00:35:35,203
Mel, hey.

592
00:35:35,306 --> 00:35:36,602
Jim, it's me.

593
00:35:36,705 --> 00:35:39,203
I need you to find Kristen
and the other kids.

594
00:35:39,307 --> 00:35:42,402
Mel, there's no signal up here.
I can't here you.

595
00:35:42,507 --> 00:35:43,600
No, hello?

596
00:35:43,707 --> 00:35:45,000
Mel?

597
00:35:45,108 --> 00:35:47,601
Oh, Jim?!

598
00:35:50,407 --> 00:35:53,703
Can you go any faster?

599
00:35:55,206 --> 00:35:58,301
We are people from different
parts of the county,

600
00:35:58,408 --> 00:36:00,300
different parts of the state,

601
00:36:00,406 --> 00:36:02,101
and we're all here this evening

602
00:36:02,207 --> 00:36:05,802
in order to honor these poor souls.

603
00:36:05,906 --> 00:36:11,703
The children of Grandview have joined
together for a lantern procession.

604
00:36:11,808 --> 00:36:13,203
Ladies and gentlemen,

605
00:36:13,307 --> 00:36:16,101
our children.

606
00:38:10,407 --> 00:38:12,003
It's ok, sweetie.

607
00:38:12,107 --> 00:38:13,501
You're safe.

608
00:38:13,605 --> 00:38:18,100
